description:
It’s a pig, it’s a plane, it’s the Superman DLC! Play as Superman himself and use powers like Super Strength, Heat Vision, and Super-Breath to take down villains and protect Metropolis. Fly to the Fortress of Solitude to explore and hang out with Krypto and grab your free Superman fan top in the Dressing Room!
